   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Carolco To Buy Back
   3.4 Million Shares
   From Its Chairman
</HL>
<DATE>
09/25/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   CRC
</CO>
<IN>
RECREATION, ENTERTAINMENT, TOYS, MOVIES, PHOTOGRAPHY, SPORTS (REC)
